name: EVA GUNDAM 01
description:
The Evangelion Unit 01 is the first non-prototype model of the Evangelion Unit.
The unit was created as a weapon to combat the Angels, and is piloted by the Third Children, Shinji Ikari.
It was the first Evangelion used in actual combat against one of them.
Here is my tribute to one of the most iconic characters in Japanese manga and anime.
